First of all,
it should start with a prologe, an introduction.
This application will run until exit command or interrupt key was pressed/used.
The list of available commands will be below
- show stats (of the player)
- show equipments
- show inventory
  - equip items / use items
  - discard items
  - inspect item(s)
- proceed map (randomize event?)
- save & exit

Array list

Equipment
- Weapon
- Armour
- Accessory

Weapon
- Shortsword
- Spear
- Handaxe

Armour
- Leather Armor
- Iron Chestplate

Items
- Equipment
- Consumable
- Key Items

Consumable
- Potion
- Herb
- Antidote

Key Items
- Tower Key
- A Letter
